not-required.name: United States
not-required.note:
Under the Compact of Free Association, visa exemption applies to citizens by birth,
former citizens of the Trust Territory of the Pacific Islands who were citizens in 1986,
naturalized spouses, children and naturalized citizens who are residents for at least 5 years,
and does not apply to those who obtained passports through passport sale.
This unlimited exemption applies for United States, Puerto Rico, Virgin Islands,
Guam and Northern Mariana Islands.
